{"tid":705202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學生獨立聯盟：悼念香港人","createTime":"2018-06-17T02:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T10:01:38.000Z","uid":28366,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1c799ebde5bc43003b28faff4bfe91a592ac940e","tid":705202,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T02:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/35415288_2102232966722741_835227824603267072_n.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=59869559f3a76ced32c698b16b74a646&amp;oe=5B770A1E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F35415288_2102232966722741_835227824603267072_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3D59869559f3a76ced32c698b16b74a646%26oe%3D5B770A1E&h=8641c8fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/35357576_2102233010056070_8067478204425699328_n.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=7c0fd7ff33ce4f3519cf91c85822f6c3&amp;oe=5BBD0208\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F35357576_2102233010056070_8067478204425699328_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3D7c0fd7ff33ce4f3519cf91c85822f6c3%26oe%3D5BBD0208&h=5a3d59c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/35360603_2102233056722732_5947604813817577472_n.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=57f642793a4c2484610824500c234b70&amp;oe=5BC364C4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F35360603_2102233056722732_5947604813817577472_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3D57f642793a4c2484610824500c234b70%26oe%3D5BC364C4&h=258211de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/35359372_2102233113389393_7188163588501012480_n.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=e5e4341bf27e99c784178134bd813a2e&amp;oe=5BA88AEF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F35359372_2102233113389393_7188163588501012480_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3De5e4341bf27e99c784178134bd813a2e%26oe%3D5BA88AEF&h=7a7d6bbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n統計2017年5月至2018年5月新聞，包括自殺死亡與企圖自殺的個案，每月平均有80-90人自殺。<br />\n<br />\n單就2018年6月4日，這個香港人悼念六四死難者的日子裡，就有3名香港人自殺；前天6月2日，更有一名13歲學生跳樓。然而，6月4日，沒有香港人關注本地人民的生死。<br />\n<br />\n到了6月8日，香港人最關注會不會掛八號。<br />\n<br />\n記憶就像過眼雲煙，倏忽即逝，卻會在下一年的同一日再次浮上心頭。所以說，香港人是最重視記憶的人，香港人是最不重視記憶的人。<br />\n<br />\n常常都有人引用米蘭．昆德拉《笑忘書》的名言，「人類對抗權力的鬥爭，就是記憶與遺忘的鬥爭。」所以對香港人來說，一年之中只有幾日是記憶戰勝了遺忘，也只有那麼幾天，香港人才能夠對抗權力。<br />\n－－－－－－－－－ 2017年Linking Park主音自殺，引起極大迴響，我頓時想起他們的一首作品《One More Light》。 &rdquo;Who cares if one more light goes out?&rdquo; 自2015年學生自殺潮開始，我就想著這一群自殺的人。每一個消逝的生靈，都是對這個世界、這個社會，用血淚投下不信任票。<br />\n<br />\n每一兩日就有人自殺，直至這些自殺的人物、自殺的數字，漸漸超出大腦記憶的容量，然後我們漸漸把這些身影遺忘。<br />\n<br />\n我無能為力，但又不忍心看著一個個香港人轉身躍下。<br />\n<br />\n有沒有人會悼念這些香港人？ &rdquo;Who cares if one more light goes out?&rdquo; &ldquo;Well, I do.&rdquo; 筆者很好奇的是，如果舉辦一個悼念香港人的集會，悼念被政權迫害入獄的香港義士、悼念被教育制度殘殺的香港學子；屆時，維園的人數會否多過六四集會的人數？"},{"pid":"b08c9774105948995e708d52eb3e89a14a7f337a","tid":705202,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T02:54:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462e9854e9f4eee39603977ce8c34432e617701b","tid":705202,"uid":294,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T02:58:46.000Z","msg":"唔震乳bot: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00298aaf99c93283403f0f7bf02172e90086e78","tid":705202,"uid":34103,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T02:59:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9188d897c16ed427dae56fddc0322bfb93e819d","tid":705202,"uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"462e9854e9f4eee39603977ce8c34432e617701b","tid":705202,"uid":294,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T02:58:46.000Z","msg":"唔震乳bot: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime