回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T07:25:07.000Z","msg":"而家做文宣講下社會現況咪做緊實事囉蔣狗<br />\n好似你喺出本土叫雞指南就做實事呀？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/17/152452_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2F152452_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ac1a7f01&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}